title: Machine Gun Kelly Lace Up Release Party | Neff
description:
Neff in collaboration with Pheed.com and BadBoy Records storm a Beverly Hills mansion to throw a party to celebrate Machine Gun Kelly's new album Lace Up.

You can purchase the Neffmau5 shirt that MGK is wearing at www.neffheadwear.com
